data.description: Begin 2024 in a beautiful home that has  so much to offer .  Located in town of Orange , close to restaurants and travel for commuting purposes.  Home has new carpeting in all 4 spacious bedrooms.  Fresh paint   in may rooms to make the home sparkle.  There is a lovely large open kitchen with center aisle and kitchen table space , and with  updated appliances as well as  access to the rear deck and fenced back yard, which includes a  large outdoor  shed.  Home boasts a formal dining room as well as large formal living room. The family room has a fireplace and lots of space for everyone to gather .  Perfect for entertaining.   This home has had many updates including new hvac system in last year, 2 recently updated bathrooms, new flooring throughout the home. Seller to find home of choice.  Large attached garage coompletes the main level space and a full unfinished basement for even more space.   So much to offer!!  Don't miss this opportunity. Pictures will be updated as soon as sellers are finished packing and moving things.
